{"tid":1824235,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"赴武漢醫院採訪肺炎疫情　無綫等港媒遭公安扣查　要求刪除攝錄片段","createTime":"2020-01-14T09:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T09:47:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"608a0a98ac397dfe935d5590569151c7e1d8abdb","tid":1824235,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"無綫新聞等多家香港傳媒，今早赴湖北武漢採訪肺炎疫情時，被公安扣查，要求刪除在醫院內拍攝的新聞素材。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎病人目前主要集中在當地傳染病專科金銀潭醫院治理。根據無綫新聞報道，該醫院內有醫護人員穿上保護衣物和戴口罩，部分前來看門診的人亦有戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，無綫等多名香港記者今早在醫院內了解情況。一批便衣公安上前問話，並將記者被帶到醫院內的警務室查問。公安要求記者刪除在醫院內拍攝的素材，交出電話和攝影器材檢查，又記錄記者證。扣查過程約一個多小時，記者其後獲放行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGxmyYD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGxmyYD.png&h=a7038bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E8%B5%B4%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E7%AD%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%92%E9%81%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%89%A3%E6%9F%A5-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2589%25A3%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=971909b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%